Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String Dim TIPO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") PONTEIRO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "_" Then ' Para todos os intrumentos (exceto PDITs)
ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 3) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5) Else ' Para PDITs ( ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 4) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 7)
End If
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & NUMERO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_2 & "')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & NUMERO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_2 & "%')"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String Dim TIPO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") PONTEIRO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "_" Then ' Para todos os intrumentos (exceto PDITs)
ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 3) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 7) Else ' Para PDITs ( ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 4) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6)
End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & NUMERO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_2 & "')" ' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & NUMERO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_2 & "%')"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
